  "special": {
    "title": "Fresh Meat!",
    "description": "On firing, each shot has a chance to add ammo back into the magazine, letting you keep shooting far longer than normal. Combined with Hyperion accuracy settling, this enables extremely consistent sustained fire and very high real-world DPS."
  },
  "notes": "If an ammo-return proc would overfill the magazine, the extra rounds can spill into reserves when there is space. Because the procs can chain, its effective magazine size varies wildly from fight to fight. It pairs especially well with ammo and fire-rate boosts, notably on Salvador. In rare cases it can bug out and stop consuming ammo or reloading correctly until you reset the area, fast travel, die, or re-equip it.",
